features: Powerful Handheld Steamer: The TICWELL Steamer takes approximately 25 seconds to heat up with the help of a 1500W heating element. The innovative professional pump and heating system allows the steam to pass through the fabric with ease, removing wrinkles thoroughly and quickly. 360 Degree Leak Proof Technology & Easy to Use: TICWELL Handheld Steamer features a unique leak, drip, and spill-proof technology, so you can steam from any angle without worrying about leaks. This Steamer supports both horizontal and vertical steam, Vertical steaming is best for removing wrinkles and horizontal steaming is best for shaping.

Removable Water Tank: The removable design makes it easy to refill the steamer. The transparent design of the water tank allows you to clearly see the remaining water, and the 15 minutes of continuous steam (250ml) allows you to remove wrinkles and straighten more clothes at once.

Elegant & Portable: The TICWELL handheld steamer is compact and has a delicate, small appearance that you can take with you when traveling. With a 7' extended power cord handheld steamer, it is perfect for home, business, and travel without having to worry about space, ensuring you have smooth fabric even during your vacation.

Perfect Present & After Sales： This package also includes 2 attachable fabric brushes and a one-piece heat-resistant ironing glove., which complements your fabric steamer perfectly. Ideal gift for your friends, family, lover, wife, parents on any occasion like Christmas, Thanksgiving, wedding. Further, our product comes with a 2-year warranty and if you are facing any issues, feel free to contact our customer care team, for a hassle-free experience.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 24, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I was looking to replace a Conair handheld steamer that didn’t get wrinkles out as much as it boasted for its 1875watts of power. I spent some time looking at some handheld steamers and after some consideration I chose this Ticwell steamer. Glad I got it! Out of the box, it was easy to remove the water tank, fill it with water, reattach it, and turn on the steamer. After about 30 seconds it was ready to go. I chose to steam a coat I just bought from Amazon. And you know that it came vacuum sealed so the coat was super creased and wrinkly. This steamer effortlessly got those creases and wrinkles out! What would have taken me 10 minutes took me 5 minutes to wrinkle-free wear. I took out some blazers that I had washed and hung dry and needed to get pressed. I used the steamer on them and because of the poly blend material determined how long you needed to spend on getting wrinkles out with this steamer.What I do love about this steamer is that it has a flat head surface with a metal plate that acts like the hot surface of an iron. Hold it against the clothing you are steaming and it acts like an iron and steams those wrinkles away. Since it doesn’t have a setting for different types of fabrics like an iron does, you might have to spend more time running the steamer head but still the time it took with my old Conair handheld I was so excited. I ran out of things to steam lol so I jumped online to write this review.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 7, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Love this little steamer
reviews.reviewText: Why did I wait so long to get a clothes steamer?! This travel steamer is awesome! I bought this for our recent vacation but didn’t realize the cruise ship doesn’t allow them. Bummer! It steams well and heats up quickly. I didn’t experience much if any spitting from the steamer and it was able to take care of all my wrinkled clothes I could throw at it. I used it so much that my husband bought me a full size one! As it is a travel one I was having to refill the water tank frequently. But again that is no fault of the steamer. It’s very easy to use and I like the self clean option it has. Just make sure to use distilled water for best results and longevity of the steamer. Overall I love it and when I can take it with me I will!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 6, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Real person here to give you the scoop on this item that I did not get for free or even at a discount. I wish.Reviewer ashwilu94 sold me with her video and I’m so glad she did. I could go on and on, but the important thing to know is this thing melts wrinkles like butter. I ordered it when I bought eight 96 inch curtain panels. I anticipated lots of stubborn wrinkles, and got lots of wrinkles, but they weren’t so stubborn with this tool. It even melted those hard creases that come from wrapping the curtain panels around a piece of cardboard. I didn’t spend more than five minutes on any one of these panels, and some of them were incredibly wrinkled. This steamer even flattened out the puckering on the edge seams of the curtain panels. It was like I ironed them, but better. I have to say I’m not too thrilled that I paid full price and now the steamer is on sale with substantial savings. Still, this thing is fabulous. I found myself looking around the house for wrinkles to destroy. I did struggle a bit with putting the water tank onto the top piece until I realized that I had to put them at a 90° angle and then twist. I’ve had no problems with mine and based on that, I would definitely recommend this all day long.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Powerful steamer! ~ gets the job done!
reviews.reviewText: I take this clothes steamer with me whenever I travel. It’s handheld, portable, and compact which is perfect to take on the go as well as store anywhere. Very easy to use. Once I fill the bottom with water it provides me enough steam to straighten 10 shirts with 15 minutes of continuous steam. Compatible with any material so I use it on everything. It only takes seconds to pre heat and no water never leaks. It came with 2 fabric brushes to help remove wrinkles, lint balls, and dirt. I like to use it right before I step out and it never leaves any water marks.
